content_html: Kathmandu, Sept 21: The annual report of the Public Service Commission (PSC) has been submitted to President Ramchandra Paudel today. The PSC Chairman Madhav Prasad Regmi presented the PSC Annual Report for Fiscal Year 2024/25 to the President in accordance with the Constitution of Nepal amidst a ceremony organized at the Office of the President
